Idemo sada korak po korak za objasnjenje svakog od ovih cvarova.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":42,"length":8,"style":"BOLD"},{"offset":64,"length":19,"style":"BOLD"},{"offset":88,"length":14,"style":"BOLD"},{"offset":42,"length":8,"style":"blue"},{"offset":64,"length":19,"style":"blue"},{"offset":88,"length":14,"style":"blue"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1qo83","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2a8pm","text":"COFYYE_ANTIREKLAMA_BLOCKCHANGENAME","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":34,"style":"BOLD"},{"offset":0,"length":34,"style":"18"},{"offset":0,"length":34,"style":"green"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4epmc","text":"","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3fa2","text":"	Ovaj cvar sluzi da blokira promenu imena dok je igrac na serveru. Vrednost 0 znaci da je iskljucena ova opcija, a vrednost 1 znaci da je ukljucena.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":1,"length":147,"style":"16"},{"offset":76,"length":1,"style":"BOLD"},{"offset":124,"length":1,"style":"BOLD"},{"offset":76,"length":1,"style":"blue"},{"offset":124,"length":1,"style":"blue"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8nv9m","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2on3f","text":"COFYYE_ANTIREKLAMA_BLOCKINCHAT","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":30,"style":"BOLD"},{"offset":0,"length":30,"style":"18"},{"offset":0,"length":30,"style":"green"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"54ri3","text":"","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4r9b8","text":"	Ovaj cvar sluzi da blokira poruku igracu u chatu ukoliko igrac napise neku IP adresu. Vrednost 0 znaci da je iskljucena ova opcija, odnosno da korisnik moze da napise IP u cha